OL,3,CBan on single-use vapes comes into
OL,4,Ceffect
OL,6,FA ban on single-use vapes in Northern
OL,7,FIreland has come into effect.
OL,9,FThe ban also came into force across
OL,10,FEngland, Scotland and Wales on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,FIt is estimated that as many as five
OL,14,Fmillion single-use vapes are thrown in
OL,15,Fbins or littered every week across the
OL,16,FUK, rather than being recycled.
