OL,3,CBan on single-use vapes comes into
OL,4,Ceffect
OL,6,FThe new restriction aims to reduce the
OL,7,Fnumber of vapes going into landfill or
OL,8,Fdiscarded as litter, where they can
OL,9,Frelease harmful substances into the
OL,10,Fenvironment and endanger wildlife.
OL,12,FIt is also intended to stop valuable
OL,13,Fresources such as cobalt, copper and
OL,14,Flithium being used in single-use
OL,15,Fdevices.
OL,17,FAgricultural, Environment and Rural
OL,18,FAffairs Minister Andrew Muir said he
OL,19,Fhopes the ban will improve the
OL,20,Fenvironment as well as the public's
OL,21,Fhealth.
