OL,3,CBan on single-use vapes comes into
OL,4,Ceffect
OL,6,F"Single-use vape waste can have a
OL,7,Fsignificant negative impact on our
OL,8,Fenvironment and biodiversity, and I
OL,9,Fwelcome this ban which will benefit
OL,10,Four environment as well as our general
OL,11,Fhealth and well-being," he said.
OL,13,F"My department as well as counterparts
OL,14,Fin the UK Government, Scotland and
OL,15,FWales have worked together to
OL,16,Fintroduce this ban concurrently, to
OL,17,Fprovide a consistent approach across
OL,18,Fthe UK for businesses as well as
OL,19,Fcustomers.
