OL,3,CBan on single-use vapes comes into
OL,4,Ceffect
OL,6,F"If you do use vapes, I would
OL,7,Fencourage you to now make it a habit
OL,8,Fnot to discard the devices and dispose
OL,9,Fof any broken or expired vapes
OL,10,Fresponsibly by taking them to your
OL,11,Flocal shop."
OL,13,FThe minister urged retailers to be
OL,14,Faware of their legal responsibility to
OL,15,Fdispose of any old stock, adding they
OL,16,Fshould offer a waste vape bin in-store
OL,17,Ffor customers to recycle any remaining
OL,18,Fdisposable units.
